Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,名字吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:03.14,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnFZZhanBiHei-M22\bord2\c&H597196&\3c&HB1D6F3&\pos(712.5,279.134)}太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家里真是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhanBiHei-M22\fsp3\frx12\fry356\frz225.5\bord0\c&H3D4154&\pos(748.122,576.849)}土豆炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈做的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.89,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhanBiHei-M22\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\pos(542.222,198.667)}给素晴君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.89,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhanBiHei-M22\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\frz2.287\pos(442.666,456.445)}可以的话吃吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.89,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhanBiHei-M22\b0\c&H000000&\bord0\pos(784,551.556)}大翔妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有这么多短时间内是没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它的名字是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 下次问素晴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小说有读者在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不能像小莓一样老老实实的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现实中我已经没有可以叫名字的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也不想跟人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对不懂人话的对象说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 龙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒哦 龙太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还是工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an2\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\pos(1103.111,432.444)\bord0\c&H9F8068&}往常的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(1022.222,437.777)}箭尾也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(939.556,423.555)}「难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(863.111,473.333)}嘟囔着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(778.667,484.888)}感受到了视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(687.111,462.666)}绿色的光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.21,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz276.6\fsp4\bord0\c&H9F8068&\pos(592.889,472.444)}闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别的资料好像是在这
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在这么狭窄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:03.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\bord0\frz287.2\move(227.543,374.514,222.545,497.455)}探索历史的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:03.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fn@FZLanTingYuan-R-GBK\an2\b1\bord0\frz288.6\move(391.906,367.968,391.273,494.546,30,5494)}飞上天空的钻石 价格的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:03.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\an2\b0\frz17.27\3c&H5145B8&\pos(1008.8,199.466)}法律的内幕和\N大人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:03.74,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1040,334.4)\frz17.41\frx8\fry4}现代指节编辑部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,名字吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我觉得取了名字也不会有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,反正要给小说里的猫起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便考虑一下你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我姑且是个作家 名字可不能乱取
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,正所谓名如其人 名字要表达出性格和特点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙的性格…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除了猫这一点以外…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 干脆让它自己来选选看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对什么有反应的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A 周
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I 伊呂波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,U 莺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,E 缘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,绢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,芥子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我究竟在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是对猫弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是对我的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底 不管是人还是动物都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fs50\frz27.68\pos(341.6,63.688)\fax0.2\clip(232,0,310,150)\c&H00BC967F}月亮和太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fs50\frz27.68\pos(341.6,63.688)\fax0.2\clip(310,0,360,150)\c&H008BEDA1}月亮和太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fs50\frz27.68\pos(341.6,63.688)\fax0.2\clip(360,0,400,150)\c&H006EFBE0}月亮和太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fs50\frz27.68\pos(341.6,63.688)\fax0.2\clip(400,0,430,150)\c&H006BC1EA}月亮和太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fs50\frz27.68\pos(341.6,63.688)\fax0.2\clip(430,0,500,150)\c&H006E8AE0}月亮和太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,给我读这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 又要读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴真是喜欢这本书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮说道 太阳似乎起床了 我去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,「月亮」是我们家的姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:18.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,注:日文中「三日月」意为新月、月牙 与男主的姓「朏」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是月亮去睡觉了 要是一直是月亮在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴晚上也要睡觉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮晚上出来 太阳白天出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们互相帮助 照亮我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 他们对彼此而言都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,阳…Haru
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,阳?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才它难道回应我了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 猫粮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人家送的赠品…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这还真是对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我都说了 这个已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在去买 所以你乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖地等我啊…阳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,它并不能理解我的意思才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 跟猫说话 大概是我脑子出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:13.76,Cat,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:20.11,Cat,,0,0,0,,我知道这个温柔又温暖的词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.68,Cat,,0,0,0,,最近才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:34.56,Cat,,0,0,0,,趴在这里的话 又暖和又舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:39.28,Cat,,0,0,0,,这是我非常中意的午睡地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:43.94,Cat,,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.10,Cat,,0,0,0,,怎么了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.95,Cat,,0,0,0,,明明是我先发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.95,Cat,,0,0,0,,绝对不会让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.96,Cat,,0,0,0,,是我赢了哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.62,Cat,,0,0,0,,什么声音这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:17.03,Cat,,0,0,0,,真是的 这么快就凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.22,Cat,,0,0,0,,不过无所谓 正好肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.81,Cat,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 我现在可是饿了就有饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.01,Cat,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.20,Cat,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这房子里真是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.44,Cat,,0,0,0,,什…什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈饭做太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过他有了这些 应该能撑一段时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.77,Cat,,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.93,Cat,,0,0,0,,刚才那是谁 是他把我的饭吃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fn@方正兰亭黑_GBK\frz177.4\frx4\fry24\pos(911.727,543.09)\3c&H666DFC&\3a&HFF&}组织正义与犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.62,Cat,,0,0,0,,真是大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.54,Cat,,0,0,0,,刚才居然想着想吃就能吃到饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.47,Cat,,0,0,0,,把有饭吃当做理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:22.67,Cat,,0,0,0,,怎么可能有这种好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.07,Cat,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要保证晾凉了啊 春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\pos(800,650)}Haru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,春家的饭很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:53.80,Cat,,0,0,0,,阳?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,春也最喜欢吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.69,Cat,,0,0,0,,是指饭吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 看小猫咪吃得这么香 我也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.90,Cat,,0,0,0,,阳…阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.86,Cat,,0,0,0,,听起来好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.59,Cat,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:25.74,Cat,,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.06,Cat,,0,0,0,,你这么想进来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.31,Cat,,0,0,0,,这里也不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.38,Cat,,0,0,0,,真是的 他一直在嘟囔什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.17,Cat,,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.66,Cat,,0,0,0,,怎么 好像安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.39,Cat,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:03.08,Cat,,0,0,0,,我知道这个温暖的词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阳?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.19,Cat,,0,0,0,,饭?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.59,Cat,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:19.33,Cat,,0,0,0,,在那边啊 饭! 饭!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.45,Cat,,0,0,0,,看吧 果然是饭的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.73,Cat,,0,0,0,,这就没了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.82,Cat,,0,0,0,,喂 你看 没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.01,Cat,,0,0,0,,我还想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.47,Cat,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖地等我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.23,Cat,,0,0,0,,没错 阳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:48.87,Cat,,0,0,0,,再多给我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:54.37,Cat,,0,0,0,,我知道 阳是吃饭的暗号对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.72,Cat,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.07,Cat,,0,0,0,,饭…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.26,Cat,,0,0,0,,这个人类 我真是搞不懂!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我买吃的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:22:59.58,Cat,,0,0,0,,吃饭啦吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,最近肩膀感觉很重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候 就赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,贴上!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\pos(640,650)}Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,贴上!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\pos(640,650)}Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:17.36,Cat,,0,0,0,,吃饭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不管三七二十一 贴上!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.11,Cat,,0,0,0,,饭在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.54,Cat,,0,0,0,,饭!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 说十遍阳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:31.38,Cat,,0,0,0,,阳阳阳阳阳阳阳阳阳阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.35,Cat,,0,0,0,,不知怎么回事肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
