Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.01,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fsp-9\bord0\c&H00809496\fnFZMiaoWu-GBK\b0\frz25.65\move(1127.444,254.444,1160.89,154.667,22,1607)}素晴喜欢\N的作家的…
